      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Used in databases like PostgreSQL and\nMariaDB to ensure durability and crash\nrecovery. Every change is first written to\nthe WAL before being applied to the actual\ndatabase and are also be used for\nreplications.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
