      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "eLxCybDAIq_snIdrfiRpE",
      "originalText": "Used in databases like PostgreSQL and MariaDB to ensure durability and crash recovery. Every change is first written to the WAL before being applied to the actual database and are also be used for replications.",
